Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.base.widget.panel Description

Contains the base implementation for panel widgets.

Client UI Base Widget Panel

This package contains the base implementation of net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.widget.panel. All implementations of that API should extend the base classes provided here.
